message.content:
Mholo! Ndiya kunceda ngendlela ekhoyo. Ngoku, ndicela ubhalele iskripthi yezi zinto ozinceda ukuzenzela:
1. Ukuthenga umntu onetyala:
   - Fumana izicelo zokuzenza isikweletu esibhalwe ngumntu onetyala.
   - Beka isikweletu esikubhalwe kwi-inbhoxi yakho yebhanki.
   - Hambisa imali kwisikweletu ngokusebenzisa i-ATM, ifoni yakho, okanye ufikelelele emahhovisi wobhanki.
2. Ukuthenga inombolo yebhanki:
   - Fumana isikweletu esibhalwe nguwe kwibhanki.
   - Beka isikweletu kwi-inbhoxi yakho yebhanki.
   - Hambisa imali kwisikweletu ngokusebenzisa i-ATM, ifoni yakho, okanye ufikelelele emahhovisi wobhanki.
3. Ukuthengisa inombolo yebhanki:
   - Fumana isikweletu somntu ongathengisiweyo.
   - Beka isikweletu kwi-inbhoxi yakho yebhanki.
   - Hambisa imali kwisikweletu ngokusebenzisa i-ATM, ifoni yakho, okanye ufikelelele emahhovisi wobhanki.
4. Ukulondoloza ikhadi lebhanki:
   - Fumana isikweletu somntu ongathengisiweyo.
   - Beka isikweletu kwi-inbhoxi yakho yebhanki.
   - Hambisa imali kwisikweletu ngokusebenzisa i-ATM, ifoni yakho, okanye ufikelelele emahhovisi wobhanki.
   - Fumana ikhadi elibhalwe nguwe.
   - B
